_:Nbcc8425812a645f8ba7ec5cf2e585d01 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Jonathan Reynolds was appointed Parliamentary Secretary to the Treasury (Chief Whip) on 5 September 2025. He was previously Secretary of State for Business and Trade and President of the Board of Trade from 5 July 2024 to 5 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was elected as the MP for Stalybridge and Hyde in May 2010.</p>\n" .
